    <main>
        <section>
        <h2>Lilja Tours: Our Story</h2>
        <p>Founded in 2021 by Julien, Lilja Tours was named after his newborn daughter, Lilja, a name symbolizing the warmth and personal connection at the heart of our travel agency. </p>
        <p>From the very beginning, our mission has been to create a truly <strong>personalized</strong> travel experience. We <strong>design your trip together with you</strong>, ensuring you're involved in the planning from start to finish. Once you arrive in Iceland, we don’t just guide you, we already know each other, making your journey feel like an adventure with friends rather than a standard tour.  </p>

    <p>In late 2024, Philippe, an experienced guide who has led many tours for Lilja Tours, joined as co-owner. Now our lead guide, he is dedicated to delivering <strong>unforgettable experiences</strong> and personally leading most of our tours.  </p>

    <p>While <strong> multiday tours</strong> remain our specialty, we also offer a variety of <strong>ready-to-book private day tours from Reykjavík</strong>, available for direct booking on this website. If you'd like to adjust any of these tours to better suit your preferences, we're always happy to customize them.  </p>

    <!--To complete your Icelandic experience, we've also **handpicked a selection of trusted local partners** offering tours we don't operate ourselves—from **ice caves and lava tunnels** to **whale watching, helicopter tours, and geothermal hot springs**. Whether you're traveling with us or on your own, **Lilja Tours is your go-to expert for unforgettable adventures in Iceland.**-->

    <picture>
        <source media="(max-width:650px)" srcset="/pictures/about/about-us-mobile.webp" width="600" height="338">
