        <section>

      <h2>Our premium fleet</h2>

     <p> Our fleet consists of two high-end vehicles, carefully selected to provide the best travel experience in Iceland.</p>

<h3>Mercedes V-Class: Comfort & Elegance</h3>  

<p>For those who value <strong>luxury and comfort</strong>, our <strong>Mercedes V-Class</strong> is the ideal choice. This spacious van accommodates up to <strong>6 passengers</strong> and features a large trunk to store your luggage with ease. Perfect for families and travelers who prefer to explore Iceland’s <strong>paved roads in style</strong>, this vehicle ensures a <strong> smooth and comfortable </strong> journey.  </p>

<img src="/pictures/cars/Mercedes-VClass.webp" alt="Blue Mercedes Van" title="Our van" width="600" height="338" loading="lazy">

<h3>Toyota Land Cruiser: Adventure-Ready</h3>

<p>For those looking to venture into Iceland’s <strong>rugged Highlands</strong>, our specially modified <strong>Toyota Land Cruiser</strong> is built for the challenge. Designed to handle the country’s <strong>legendary F-Roads</strong>, this <strong>off-road powerhouse</strong> ensures a <strong>safe and smooth</strong> ride through even the most remote landscapes. With a maximum capacity of <strong>4 passengers</strong>, it’s the perfect choice for those who seek <strong>adventure without compromising on comfort</strong>. </p>



<img src="/pictures/cars/Toyota-LandCruiser.webp" alt="Toyota Land Cruiser" title="Our toyota LandCruiser" width="600" height="338" loading="lazy">

        </section>

        <section>
            <h2>Our team</h2>
            <p>Our team is small but deeply passionate about Iceland and dedicated to providing exceptional travel experiences.  </p>
            <h3>Julien – Travel Designer & Founder</h3>
            <p>Julien has called Iceland home since 2016. A true <strong>outdoor enthusiast</strong>, he spent <strong>six incredible years guiding travelers across the country</strong>, exploring its every hidden gem. With an <strong>in-depth knowledge of Iceland’s landscapes, culture, and nature</strong>, he now focuses on <strong>crafting unforgettable journeys</strong>, ensuring that every trip is tailored to perfection.</p>  
                <img src="/pictures/Julien-CEO-Founder-Guide.webp" alt="Founder of Lilja Tours" title="CEO" width="600" height="338" loading="lazy" style="border-radius: 50%; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; height: auto; max-width: 20rem;">
                <h3>Philippe – Lead Guide & Co-Owner</h3>
                <p>Philippe has been an integral part of <strong>Lilja Tours</strong> from its early days, regularly guiding our tours. Now a <strong>co-owner and lead guide</strong>, he is the first to be assigned to our tours—so chances are, you'll find him <strong>behind the wheel, ready to take you on an adventure!</strong> In addition to guiding, Philippe also ensures that our <strong>vehicles remain in top-notch condition</strong> and that everything runs smoothly for your journey in Iceland.</p>  
                    <img src="/pictures/Philippe-Owner-Guide.webp" alt="Lead guide of Lilja Tours" title="CEO" width="600" height="338" loading="lazy" style="border-radius: 50%; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; height: auto; max-width: 20rem;">
